<emphasis id="B906EAB7935B8E06F2AAF82AFE73F819" box="[151,418,1976,2002]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="486">
<collectingMunicipality id="6BA9ACDF935B8E06F2AAF82AFF79F819" box="[151,168,1976,2002]" pageId="2" pageNumber="486">Il</collectingMunicipality>
se trouve au 
<collectingCountry id="F3657635935B8E06F303F82AFE73F819" box="[318,418,1976,2002]" name="Portugal" pageId="2" pageNumber="486">Portugal</collectingCountry>
</emphasis>
with regard to the locality
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C368652E935B8E07F2FAF84EFCA1FF32" lastPageId="3" lastPageNumber="487" pageId="2" pageNumber="486" type="reference_group">
<paragraph id="8BCD36A5935B8E07F2FAF84EFC94FF1E" blockId="2.[151,1436,1832,2039]" lastBlockId="3.[151,1436,151,249]" lastPageId="3" lastPageNumber="487" pageId="2" pageNumber="486">
<taxonomicName id="4C724D26935B8E06F2FAF84EFE7CF83D" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1830" box="[199,429,2012,2038]" class="Insecta" family="Curculionidae" genus="Carterus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="486" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="interceptus">
<emphasis id="B906EAB7935B8E06F2FAF84EFE7CF83D" box="[199,429,2012,2038]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="486">Carterus interceptus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is well differentiated from other congeneric taxa by the deeply notched labrum at middle, together with mandible details, peculiar ligula and paraglossa, large body size, etc. (e.g., 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B54935A8E07F6AAFF05FAFEFF7A" author="Fuente de la, J. M." box="[1175,1327,151,177]" pageId="3" pageNumber="487" refId="ref10490" refString="Fuente de la, J. M. (1927) Tablas analiticas para la clasificacion de los coleopteros de la Peninsula Iberica. Adephaga: I Cicindelidae, II Carabidae. J. Bosch, Barcelona, 415 pp." type="book" year="1927">Fuente, 1927</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B54935A8E07F706FF05FF02FF1E" author="Antoine, M." pageId="3" pageNumber="487" pagination="315 - 465" refId="ref10238" refString="Antoine, M. (1959) Coleopteres Carabiques du Maroc. Troisieme partie. Memoires de la Societe des Sciences Naturelles et Physiques du Maroc, Nouvelle Serie, Zoologie, 6, 315 - 465." type="journal article" year="1959">Antoine, 1959</bibRefCitation>
). These characters are well represented in the 
<typeStatus id="54C98807935A8E07F0EAFF29FC90FF1E" box="[727,833,187,213]" pageId="3" pageNumber="487">lectotype</typeStatus>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BCD36A5935A8E07F2FAFF4DFCA1FF32" blockId="3.[151,1436,151,249]" box="[199,880,223,249]" pageId="3" pageNumber="487">The species shows an Ibero-Maghrebian distribution pattern.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
